    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>It's time to celebrate the 2025 Home Run Derby at MLB's All-Star Week in Atlanta!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check out Truist Park, now decorated for baseball's biggest week, plus unlock new All-Star-themed batskins.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GO BIG in MLB’s Home Run Derby VR!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the only officially licensed Major League Baseball game in VR!  Every team, every ballpark, right here and no place else.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience the Thrill of a Real Home Run Derby:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Visceral Gameplay:</strong> Feel the crack of the bat every swing with realistic physics and intuitive motion controls. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Real MLB Ballparks:</strong> Crush towering home runs in authentically rendered ballparks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the Best: Compete against other players as you climb the leaderboards and earn incentives.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Progression &amp; Customization Options:</strong> Advance through a deep progression system, unlocking unique bats, gloves, trophies and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build a Legacy:</strong> Invite friends to your custom clubhouse, decorated with earned items showcasing your big accomplishments and unique style.  Plus: Watch the latest MLB news and highlights on the big screen from the best seat in the house!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More Than Just a Game, it's a Major League Baseball Experience:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Home Run Derby VR</i> puts you in the heart of baseball's most electrifying contest. Step into the batter's box, grip your virtual bat and unleash your inner slugger in a stunning, immersive VR experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Download Home Run Derby VR today and become a legend!</h2>",
